    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Real.le_sin#doc\">docs#Real.le_sin</a> and <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Real.sin_le#doc\">docs#Real.sin_le</a> could be helpful</p>",
