    {
        "content": "<p>Alternatively if you want to go about doing some kind of derivatives argument on neighbourhoods of zero, there’s a bunch of useful results <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/MeanValue.html#exists_deriv_eq_slope\">in the mean value theorem file</a></p>",
